snippet.textDisplay:
The force has never been fully explained in what it can, and can't do.
If we base what the force can do from A New Hope, It allows you to sense things, and effect peoples minds. That is all. That is all that was shown in A New Hope in regards to the force. No Force push/Pull, not moving rocks, no lightning. Each movie expands on what the force can do. New force abilities are shown with every new Star Wars Movie/Show/Game.
Saying "The Force can't do that" is meaningless since it is up to the writers what it can and can't do. It's like who will win in a fight, Superman or Batman. Either would win, it depends on the writer.
